list_bullet_points.text:
(1) a method to track key information for each asset, including, as applicable, the 
following: 
  (i) owner; 
  (ii) location; 
(iii) classification or sensitivity; 
(iv) support expiration date; and 
(v) recovery time objectives; and

implement risk-based policies, procedures and controls designed to monitor the 
activity of authorized users and detect unauthorized access or use of, or tampering with, 
nonpublic information by such authorized users;
